 the purchase of healthcare products\nwithin health departments in each State and Territory.	focuses on developing national health information management and communication technology standards. Its work includes creating frameworks for interoperability, standardizing clinical communications, establishing unique healthcare identifiers, and preparing standards for individual electronic health records, identity management, secure messaging, and supply chain management.	\N
